            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">47.507</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2820e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2834e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d2820e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2834e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1046560.dita#i1046560"
                              base="i1046560"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.247-64</xref>, Preference for Privately Owned U.S.-Flag Commercial Vessels, in solicitations and contracts that may involve ocean transportation of supplies subject to the Cargo Preference Act of1954. (For application of the Cargo Preference Act of1954, see <xref href="FAR-i1069815.dita#i1069815"
                              base="i1069815"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.502</xref>(a)(3), <xref href="FAR-i1069836.dita#i1069836"
                              base="i1069836"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.503</xref>(a), and <xref href="FAR-i1069858.dita#i1069858"
                              base="i1069858"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.504</xref>.)</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2834e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                If an applicable statute requires, or if it has been determined under agency procedures, that the supplies to be furnished under the contracts must be transported exclusively in privately owned U.S.-flag commercial vessels (see <xref href="FAR-i1069815.dita#i1069815"
                              base="i1069815"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.502</xref>(a)(1) and <xref href="FAR-i1069836.dita#i1069836"
                              base="i1069836"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.503</xref>(b)), use the clause with its AlternateI.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2834e63" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Except for contracts or agreements for ocean transportation services or construction contracts, use the clause with its AlternateII if any of the supplies to be transported are commercial items that are shipped in direct support of U.S. military-</p>
							              <ol id="d2820e69" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2834e73" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Contingency operations;</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2834e82" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Exercises; or</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2834e91" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Forces deployed in connection with United Nations or North Atlantic Treaty Organization humanitarian or peacekeeping operations.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2834e104" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer may insert in solicitations and contracts, under agency procedures, additional appropriate clauses concerning the vessels to be used.</p>
					          <p id="d2834e110" class="- topic/p "/>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
